    "description": "Join the Union Bank of India Ventures Solutions family as a Credit Analyst in Hyderabad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Union Bank of India Ventures Solutions:\nUnion Bank of India Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Hyderabad, Telangana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Union Bank of India Ventures Solutions!",
